Applications of Data Science.


+ Data Science helps physicians provide the best treatment for their patients, 
    and helps meteorologists predict the extent of local weather events, 
    and can even help predict natural disasters like earthquakes and tornadoes.

+ That companies can start on their data science journey by capturing data. 
    Once they have data, they can begin analysing it.

+ Some ways that data is generated by consumers. 

+ How businesses like Netflix, Amazon, UPs, Google, 
    and Apple use the data generated by their consumers and employees.

+ The purpose of the final deliverable of a Data Science project is 
    to communicate new information and insights from the data analysis to key decision-makers.
